{"tid":1906161,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個，你曾經聽錯過最離譜既經歷","createTime":"2020-03-01T17:42:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T19:09:16.000Z","uid":123335,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bd5530b0e65eecc7357fec4948d1bdad37cf7b3d","tid":1906161,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T17:42:56.000Z","msg":"話說當年我讀中學有宗教堂<br />\n有日教書，個miss 係啦啦講「牧師林」<br />\n我心諗：邊撚個森林有咁多牧師咁on9呀？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為本身我都算係壞學生黎，好少會溫書，更何況係宗教書 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我一直多年黎都冇去 fact check 個事實<br />\n淨係一直都記住：<br />\n【當年宗教MISS 講過有個森林，入面住左好多牧師】<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然之後因為讀唔成書，公開試考得太差 <br />\n就去左外國讀野雞U <br />\n果邊D人講英文，所以唔會聽到牧師林呢個Term <br />\n<br />\n3年後，<br />\n我由外國回流返香港 <br />\n我終於係香港唔知邊篇新聞報導 <br />\n第一次見到「穆斯林」呢個 Term <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed850e5d415684eedd0a24b2834ee3a7d5568994","tid":1906161,"uid":244329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit